Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:01:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to continue traveling with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that moment is the only\Nchance to come aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... Karoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It All Started on That Day!\NVivi Tells the Story of Her Adventure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram! I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be Queen of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Igaram, good morning.\NWhat's wrong? You're all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can't just barge in like that!\NVivi-sama is changing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... well, uhm... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, do you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah, no...\N--I told you to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow... I guess it was just my imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, King. You were there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, Terracotta-san is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this too tight, Terracotta-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how a princess' formal attire is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Square\Nis already full of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was announced that\Nyour speech starts at 10:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're being really impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do understand how they feel, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is your coming-of-age\Nceremony that we've waited 2 years for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under normal circumstances, this would\Nhave been held when you were 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have anything\Nimpressive to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is show everyone\Nhow much you've grown. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coming-of-age ceremony is held\Nto celebrate you becoming an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please consider the King's feelings\Nin taking the trouble to hold it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes... I heard that your speech today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be broadcast throughout Alabasta\Nusing transponder snails and amplifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a report that a\Nbattle started at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,\Nwe can no longer get involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Shoot cannonballs!\NThen I could repel them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep taking these iron\Nspears on the ship's bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be just a matter of time before we sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here come more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I can't keep plugging\Nthe holes any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes all our effort\Njust to protect one side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One ship against eight isn't a fair fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this was close combat,\Nwe'd have a better chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we chase them or run away,\Nthey'll never change this formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Black Cage Unit's specialty,\Nthe "Black Spear Formation"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not good enough\Nto break it! Idiots! You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hypnotist! You're a pirate, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I have my reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one on the left...\NWhere do I know him from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That annoying violent cook and his gang...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sink them here today! I've powered up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, stare at this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally prove today that I'm not a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Busy, busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One...! Two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Did you do that?! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O... Okay! It was just as I calculated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens to\Nships once I'm on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nosie, that was amazing! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships in the south sank! Now we\Ncan break through there in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon Clay-sama! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Black Cage" is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Black Cage Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a captain at Navy Headquarters\Nand this area is under her jurisdiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real pain.\NWe'll hurry up and fly the coop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we've\Nweakened them quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no ship that we can't take down\Nusing our Black Cage Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away.\NWhen dealing with guys like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you take them lightly,\Nyou'll end up getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we pull up, you guys stay back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or you'll be in my way. That'd annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing?! We have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we pass through that point in the south,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to escape\Nwith minimum damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't change course,\Nthey'll take us down for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna go, then go. We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon Clay-sama! Please hurry!\NLet's get out of here ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noon at the eastern harbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to go around,\Nso we have to dash through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... that's ludicrous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some treasure worth\Nyour lives there or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go ahead and die, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going there to pick up our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... So it's for your pal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in, okay, Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi, what did you want to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mistook you for the Queen\Nwhen she was young, Vivi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a seat, Daddy--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, Father... Igaram...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something important\Nto talk with you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running now wouldn't be like Bon Clay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--If we abandon pals who would\Nrisk their lives to pick up their pal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will we... be able to enjoy\Nour food tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys... Straw Hats, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what I have to say carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hina! They're dividing their forces!\NThe duck ship is going south!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The duck is probably a decoy in any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Actually, all the\NStraw Hats are on the duck ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sheep ship is the decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow them! Return to\Nthe formation immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the Straw Hat you guys're looking for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hina! The sheep ship\Nis heading to the east!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were tricked, weren't you?! We're\Nexperts at disguising ourselves! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're the Straw Hats' friends...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go astray as a man...\NEven if I go astray as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't go astray as a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are to fall, we'll fall\Ntogether into the true sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it bloom... Oh, come my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By... Bon Clay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm humiliated...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-chan... We'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are to fall, let it be in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flower of friendship... is rejoicing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know the ringleader?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... It's a so-called\Nunderground organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for their boss, even its members\Nknow nothing about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's... the enemy of this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already impossible for us to gain\Ninformation on them from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, further investigation\Nwill only put the country at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've got a lead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram, do you know what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I don't! I-I have to go back to my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Igaram!\N--No! This isn't a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's all the more reason to, Igaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit around and do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! They're after us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess Vivi!\N--It's Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Vivi-sama. Let me\Nask you just one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared not to lay down your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had... a little adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The princess's speech has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I've been waiting!\N--So she was really okay. I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony in Alubarna has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was delayed by two hours. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I hope it won't cause a commotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza! Hey, Koza! Come out!\NVivi-chan's speech has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amplifier is cranked all the way up.\NShe can be heard anywhere in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a journey... to cross the\Ndark sea in search of "despair."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I left the country,\NI saw such a vast sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on that sea, I found\Nunbelievable, thriving islands...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creatures I had never seen before...\NSceneries I could barely consider real...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times, the melody\Nof the waves was quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...swaying gently, as if\Neasing my small worries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other times, the melody was violent...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...laughing at me, as if it would\Ntear apart my weak heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that dark, dark storm,\NI encountered a single, small, ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship said to me,\Nwhile pushing me onwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can't you see that light?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wondrous ship, which never\Nlost its way even in darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,danced its way across the huge waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship didn't fight the sea, but its\Nstem was pointed straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even during a headwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ship pointed and said,\N"Look! There's a light!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,History will soon call this an illusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to me, it is the only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the Navy that she secretly fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the speech, right?\NIt was Vivi's voice without doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just broadcasting the\Nceremony being held in Alubarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already decided that\Nshe wouldn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that voice just resembled\NVivi's voice. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Tamarisk place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. It's past noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that she didn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out and look for her!\NShe's definitely here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is bad! The Navy is after us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many ships are there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! We're gonna sail out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, Luffy. Her case\Nis different from ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, show your face, fake princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Squad Captain Igaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the real Vivi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the princess speaking from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can throw pretty far...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Vivi!\N--See?! She came!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back! Better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is right there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo, give me the handset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... go with you!\NThank you so much for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Is that the princess of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be at the ceremony in Alubarna...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go on more adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no ignoring...\Nthat I love this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Vivi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it, Squad Captain Igaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice dancing, Squad Captain Igaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Keep it up!\N--We came here to see Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're to put a sign,\NI'd want it to be an "X."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?\N--We're pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it actually means "death"\Nto your opponents, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! I want it to be an "X"!\NRight, Vivi? It looks cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I like it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what it is.\NJust write it. That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will remain here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sign of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if we ever meet again some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will you call me your friend again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that? That princess\Nis connected with the Straw Hats...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess is a friend\Nof pirates?! Can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You'll forever be our...\N--Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't reply! The Navy has noticed Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we prove she's connected with us,\Nshe'll become a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's part without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, this thing on\Nour left arm is the sign of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I run towards\Nto see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the helm and opened the\Nmiraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for the sky and sought out\Nmy dreams, though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream; when I met you,\NI discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a bit of courage,\NI gained something grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for my "wish"\Nto become my "pledge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the tale of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my feelings\Nin a brand new wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase after you\Nwherever you go, Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san and the others are gone now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the important\Nthings I learned on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to work hard for the future\Nof this country. Okay, Karoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll find wonderful new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scent Of Danger!\NThe Seventh Member is Nico Robin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
